title: Frankie Boyle's New World Order S01E02
description:
Frankie Boyle's New World Order S01E02 (720p HD, soft Eng subs)

Following the successful Scottish Referendum, Election and American Autopsy specials for BBC iPlayer, Frankie Boyle returns to BBC2 with his New World Order to help make sense of the bewildering world we live in. 

 In a time where Donald Trump can be president, who better to dissect the week's news than Frankie Boyle. The show features Frankie at his brilliant best doing stand-up, review, discussion and audience interaction - all in an attempt to make sense of what's going on around us. Each week Frankie makes a series of bold and often outrageous statements about the week's news. He is joined by a range of guests, including comics and experts, who are on hand to take him to task over his claims.

This week, Frankie is joined by Sara Pascoe and Katherine Ryan.

(with soft subtitles) 

First broadcast: 16 June 2017
Duration:  30 minutes
